summary: Adds a small camp on a rooftop in Riften right near the Mistveil Keep
descriptionHtml:
Hello! Godfather123 here with my first mod for Skyrim!
This adds a small Rooftop camp right next to Mistveil keep,
It is pretty small with no custom interior, but it is meant for a small place to relax in Riften!
Features:
A small camp on a Rooftop in Riften
A bed
A Firepit with a cooking spit
A personal chest (WARNING! I AM NOT THE BEST MODDER, BUT I MAY HAVE DONE IT WRONG! PLEASE SAVE BEFORE PLACING ITEMS IN IT BECAUSE IT MAY DESPAWN!)
A new food item: Nightingale Wine, with good buffs
A small book on the lore of the place.
Some thieving books
author: Godfather123
